
Functionality:
Odds Advisor - assess whether the given odds are worth taking a risk and how much they are profitable or loss likely.

control - OddsAdvisorPanel on the PlayerVsPlayer and PlayerStats forms

PlayerVsPlayer form:

after picking the players, enter the values of odds for each player. Click 'Assess' -> the application finds probabilities for either of the players and
recalculates them to the given odds. It also tells what are the deviations of the bookmaker's odds to the calculated odds.

PlayerStats form:

after picking the player, enter the value of the odds. Click 'Assess' -> the application will do similar calculations to the above.

OddsAssecor class will take care of the calculations.